{"tid":2344971,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"無端端生左個b","createTime":"2020-12-29T07:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T10:36:05.000Z","uid":147855,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a62a6cd3ff0e8cf4aec79add75bb33b8458308f0","tid":2344971,"uid":147855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:16:11.000Z","msg":"今朝換水無意中發現一條極細既魚仔係度游<br />\n初初仲以為眼花<br />\n因為啲孔雀魚好似仲好細條<br />\n完全唔覺佢哋大左肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到而家生完我都唔知邊隻生<br />\n係有幾條個肚特別大<br />\n但佢哋幾個月前個肚已經咁大<br />\n仲特別大食 所以一路當佢哋係死肥豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jk37tEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjk37tEL.jpg&h=951d8af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過得一條 唔知其他是咪已經俾其他魚食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b800c58d604aa10fa7f9060886b67f3c2ec95aa6","tid":2344971,"uid":360907,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇張圖心諗：你影緊乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁細隻要點養？食乜？"},{"pid":"bfe0628970098a332a53e5c98caa5e52256514d8","tid":2344971,"uid":147855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b800c58d604aa10fa7f9060886b67f3c2ec95aa6","tid":2344971,"uid":360907,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇張圖心諗：你影緊乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁細隻要點養？食乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"考眼力遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我將啲魚糧磨成粉咁餵咋<br />\n但佢好似未食<br />\n可能啱啱出世無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"